					<description><![CDATA[When I&#8217;m not writing, sometime I enjoy a bit of The Sims 3.  With all of the fine, detailed controls in the game that let you create exactly the face and body shape you want for your character, it was only a matter of time before I tried to create the Twist I see in [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-240 alignright" title="Money Shot" alt="Money shot" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/money-shot.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="221" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/money-shot.jpg 515w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/money-shot-300x221.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />When I&#8217;m not writing, sometime I enjoy a bit of <a href="http://www.thesims3.com/" target="_blank">The Sims 3</a>.  With all of the fine, detailed controls in the game that let you create exactly the face and body shape you want for your character, it was only a matter of time before I tried to create the Twist I see in my mind&#8217;s eye.  Here&#8217;s the result!</p>
<p>This Simy is eerily close to the face that I originally imagined for Twist.  Only, there aren&#8217;t any good period costumes in my version of the game, and I imagined him with curlier hair.  Is this Simy anything like the man you see when you read CWTwist?  Leave a comment and let me know.  I&#8217;d love to find out what you envision!</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft  wp-image-238" style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:0;" title="*gasp!*" alt="aaa" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aaa.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="222" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aaa.jpg 515w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aaa-300x221.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft  wp-image-242" title="Wide shot" alt="wide shot" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/wide-shot.jpg?w=225" width="203" height="269" /></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft  wp-image-239" title="Blue Steel" alt="" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blue-steel.jpg?w=225" width="203" height="270" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blue-steel.jpg 286w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/blue-steel-225x300.jpg 225w" sizes="(max-width: 203px) 100vw, 203px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft  wp-image-241" style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:0;" title="#smug" alt="smug" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/smug.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="222" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/smug.jpg 515w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/smug-300x221.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
